description:
Join the world of Fast & Furious with HOT WHEELS UNLEASHED™ 2! 
This pack is inspired by Fast X, the latest chapter in the global blockbuster Fast & Furious saga, and is made for those who live on pure adrenaline and know how to race. Your collection definitely wants the power of these all-muscle and unstoppable cars.
The iconic El Camino, the all-Italian jewel Alfa Romeo Giulia Sprint GTA, the aggressive BMW M5 and the drifting specialist Datsun 240Z are ready to hit the virtual road!

This DLC includes:
- El Camino
- Alfa Romeo Giulia Sprint GTA
- BMW M5
- Datsun 240Z

This DLC is included in the HOT WHEELS UNLEASHED™ 2 - Season Pass Vol. 1.
name: HOT WHEELS UNLEASHED™ 2 - Fast X Pack
